    "text": [
        "Dear Sneha,",
        "It's great to hear that you are enrolling your child to music class. I am writing  this letter to inform that as per request, I found a very talented and hard-working teacher Ms Hema.",
        "Ms . Hema is a renowned classical teacher at the Drona music academy. She has 15 years of total experience in classical music and also she is a certified dancer.She Can teach dance as well to your offspring , for example, Kathak or Kuchipudi .",
        "I feel she will be the most suitable teacher because of her experience for sure , but also she is teacher in primary school so she is well aware of how to teach beginners and small kids.Additionally, she lives near to your house which will help you to drop off and pick up your kid before and after classes.",
        "Now , if you want to connect with her , you can contact her directly as I referred you and also you can mail her and discuss  fees and timing.",
        "Hope it helps and do let me know if you need any other help.",
        "Warm Regards",
        "Pooja"
